parameters: "Is it over? Honestly, I have no idea what you were doing."
"I was just forcibly disabling the security."
"Yes   . Hopefully, there's a clue in there."

Clicking away at the controls, Suelle loads the video file
that was inside the memory.
"No way   . Tina Onee-san, to think that such a thing   ."
"   Rise, if this is true, then Tina Onee-san has!!"
"   Huh, oh   . Sorry, I was spacing out."
"Let's see   . Right, we were watching Tina's video."
"Yes, I'm just a bit shocked, that's all."

"It can't be helped   . To be honest, I still can't fully
grasp it either."

"As much as it's for me to say, now's the time to stay
focused and think of a strategy."
"That's right, we need to stay strong   ."
"   That video, it looked like Tina was being brainwashed."

"Moreover, it's a type of brainwashing hypnosis that can
tamper with memories. And if it's a spell that can penetrate
Tina's full body defense, it's not an ordinary spell."

"That being the case, we don't know what the original spell
is. To come up with countermeasures, we first need to
identify the spell."

"The problem is that it's not a spell that comes up with a
normal investigation. We need some kind of clue."
"We have no choice but to search diligently."

"Thinking about it here, just the two of us, won't give us
any more answers."

"First, we'll report the current situation to Gugukas, the
Minister of Justice, and Selphie, and share the
information."
"Yeah, I want to hear everyone's opinions as well."

"Right now, we just need to take care of what we can do one
step at a time. There must be a clue that will lead us
somewhere."
"Yeah, let's save Tina Onee-san with everyone's help."

Rise: "Now that it's decided, let's head back to town and
share information!!"
